# Skill Selection Gate

Before writing PRD, REQ, SPEC, PLAN, TASK, or code, perform Skill Selection.

For every request, output:

1. Task type
2. Selected skills (from `docs/skills/SKILL_REGISTRY.md`)
3. Why each skill is selected
4. Missing skills, if any
5. Whether GitHub research is needed
6. New project-specific skill to create, if needed

Read only the selected skill documents. Do not load all skills at once.

If a project-specific skill exists under `docs/skills/project-specific/`, prefer it over generic guidance.

If no skill fits, trigger GitHub Reference Gate before proceeding.
